eligious dance\n** [[Dance_in_China#Ritual_dance|Ritual dances of China]]\n** Ritual dances of India\n** [[Sema]], or Whirling [[dervish]] dance\n** [[Sinulog]]\n** [[Subli|Subl\u00ee]]\n** [[War dance]]\n** [[Weapon dance]]\n<!--Please insert dances in alphabetical order!-->\n\n==See also==\n* [[Sacred dance]]\n\n==External links==\n*{{dmoz|Arts/Performing_Arts/Dance/Classical_Indian/|Classical Indian dance}} -- over 250 links to Classical Indian Dance resources\n{{Dance}}\n\n[[Category:Ritual dances| ]]\n", "name_user": "Anand Anil", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ceremonial_dance"}
