.htm|title=The Government strongly condemns violent acts|website=www.info.gov.hk|access-date=2020-03-09|date=2020-07-22|quote=Meanwhile in Yuen Long, some people congregated at the platforms of the MTR station and train compartments, attacking commuters. It led to confrontations and injuries.}}</ref>, violent acts<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/22/P2019072200890.htm?fontSize=1|title=Transcript of remarks by CE at media session (with video)|website=www.info.gov.hk|access-date=2020-03-09|date=2020-07-22|quote=At the time when we issued that statement about the Yuen Long violent acts}}</ref> and assault cases<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/22/P2019072200117.htm|title=Police condemn violent acts|website=www.info.gov.hk|access-date=2020-03-09|date=2020-07-22|quote=Meanwhile, assault cases also happened in Yuen Long.}}</ref>\n* <small> Folk Classification: </small>[[terrorist attack]]<ref name=\"apple-2019-07-22b\">{{cite news|title=\u6c88\u65ed\u6689\u5f15\u570b\u969b\u6a19\u6e96 \u6307\u5143\u6717\u7121\u5dee\u5225\u6253\u4eba\u300c\u662f\u4e00\u5834\u6050\u8972\u300d |url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190722/59849879 |accessdate=22 July 2019 |work=Apple Daily |language=zh|date=22 July 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190722081739/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190722/59849879 |archive-date=22 July 2019 |url-status=live|quote= If the Yuen Long case happened in other places, it would be defined as a Terrorist Attack. Leader will label it, investigate the case seriously, and to use any means to stabilize the society.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/07/24/protest-yuen-long-terror-attack-set-saturday-us-raises-concerns-violence/|title=Protest in Yuen Long against 'terror attack' set for Saturday, as US raises concerns over violence|date=2019-07-24|website=Hong Kong Free Press HKFP|language=en|access-date=2020-03-09}}</ref